# Buruja — commit only the deployable site (public/) + build tooling/config.
# The ~46 GB of source content, social-media renders, audio, video, book PDFs,
# and the SalatTid.se sub-brand stay local (regenerable / hosted on R2 separately).

# Ignore everything at the repo root by default...
/*

# ...then re-include exactly what the repo should track:
!/.gitignore
!/README.md
!/build.py
!/seo.py
!/make_assets.py
!/public/
!/wrangler.toml

# OS / cache junk (belt and suspenders, even inside tracked dirs)
.DS_Store
__pycache__/
*.pyc
